We will offer them active monitoring, and if the disease begins to progress, we will begin treatment.
Increasingly, we are determining with precision the criteria for deciding who should or should not undergo a course of treatment.
I would recommend that you take the test anyway.
But it’s also important to consult your doctor to determine whether or not you should take this test.
