It can be, for example, laser sensors, they give a good resolution in depth, it is very important.
- If we talk about your work with Xbox Kinect sensors, what are your complaints about modern cameras?
Lack of resolution, depth, or something else?
“In principle, the current generation is something that we can build on in our work on three-dimensional recognition.
